d persons\u003C/change> \n\t\u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic001421_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dellвҖҷIdentitГ  Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dellвҖҷIdentitГ  Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic001421.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dellвҖҷIdentitГ  Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dellвҖҷIdentitГ  Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#VM\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>\u003Cunclear>Оҡ\u003C/unclear>ОұО»О№ОәПҒО¬П„ОөМ„ПӮ\u003C/name> ОәОұО»бҪё\u003Cunclear>ПӮ\u003C/unclear> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">бҪҒ\u003C/supplied> \u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname type=\"patronym\">\u003Cunclear>Оҡ\u003C/unclear>\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\" cert=\"low\">ПҒОұ\u003C/supplied>ПғОҜПҖОҝП…\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>\u003C/persName> ОәОұбҪ¶ \u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>ОӣОҝМ„ПғОұО№ПӮ\u003C/name> \u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>бјҲОјОҝП…ОҪПҶОҜ\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\" break=\"no\"/>ОҝМ„\u003Cunclear>ОҪ\u003C/unclear>ОҝПӮ\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>\u003C/persName> П„ОҝОәОөНӮПӮ НұОҝОҜ ОәвҖҷ бј”О»ОұОІОҝОҪ ПҮОҝМ„МҒПҒОөМ„\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">ОҪ\u003C/supplied> НұОҝНӮО№ НұОҝМ„ПӮ ОјОҪОөМ„МҒОјОұ ОјОөбҝ–ОҪ\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\" break=\"no\"/>ОұО№ ОәОұбҪ¶ НұОҝМ„ПӮ\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003Cp>After Manganaro 1996\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Capp loc=\"1\">\n                \u003Cnote>Jeffery Archive: ОҡОұО»О№ОәПҒО¬П„ОөМ„ПӮ ОәОұО»бҪё\u003Cunclear>ПӮ\u003C/unclear> НұОҝ П„Оҝ [ОәОұО»]ОҜПҖОҝП… ОҪОҝОёОҝПӮ бјҲО№ПғОұ ОңОҝП…ОҪПҶОҜ\u003C/note>\n            \u003C/app>\n            \u003Capp loc=\"2\">\n                \u003Cnote>Jeffery Archive: ОјОө[О»]ОөОҪ ОұОјОөО№ОҪОҝ\u003C/note>\n            \u003C/app>\n            \u003Capp loc=\"3\">\n                \u003Cnote>Jeffery Archive: -ОҪ ОәОұбҪ¶ НұОҝМ„ПӮ ОұОјвҖҷОөО№{ОҪ}ОұО№\u003C/note>\n            \u003C/app>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--translation(s) - add @xml:lang for 'en' or 'it' to div-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--commented out pending revision-->\n                    \u003C!--epitaph of Kalikrates and? Mang attempts a full restoration, but Dubois, BE 1997 thinks it tenuous! Cf. Curbera's re-ed. The name Nounphion is v. rare. This not a true funerary inscr., but rather records the acquisition of plot of land for the grave. Located by AMM 31.03.15.-->\n                    \u003C!-- J.WC. Kamar.15b p.01(2)-02(2): В«Seems to be a legal document, on the acquisition of the 2 parents of an area for the tomb (ПҮПүПҒО·!) of their son Mounphin (should read Monphin) and themselves. The parents \n                    are Kallik. and Aisa, K. be called bastard of Kallippos, viz. had Sikel mother? [...] till we get a good copy, my reading very doubtfulВ». -->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>46.1260.2\u003C/citedRange>\n            